adoptionList.name: Simba
adoptionList.description: Simba has always lived with an old lady but can no longer take care of him, so that he did not end up in the kennel we have taken over. He is a calm and adult dog, he does not know what it is to live in a shelter when he was always in a house. He does not deserve to finish his last years without a family.

adoptionList.name: Bones
adoptionList.description: Bones is alone again.This little boy entered the ward in 2014, and a few months later he was adopted.He found someone who cared for him, and both loved each other as one can only want a dog and a good person. The owner has died in an accident and Bones has been left alone. Unfortunately, now all we can do is fight so that as soon as possible I will be with a family again. We know it will be soon because an angel will undoubtedly continue to take care of him.

adoptionList.name: Elsa
adoptionList.description: Elsa is a dog that we took out of the kennel, we had gone to pick up another dog when we passed near her cageMonths and we saw her cornered and shaking. We could not leave her there. It is very good and quiet.It is major, we have done a general and disease analysis to see how it is, and is very healthy. This grandmother needs a family I assure you that you will fall in love with her, she is super grateful.

adoptionList.name: Lima
adoptionList.description: Lima lived all his life in a school farm where he was happy and welcomed with affection all those who passed by, whether they were people or animals. Now she is with us, she is safe again, however she remains very sad, longs for her former owners and does not stop losing her fear. That is why it is important that you find a home as soon as possible where you can trust in the human being again. She is very good and sociable.

adoptionList.name: Sira
adoptionList.description: We have to find her family, she is an admirable, good and affectionate dog, beautiful and playful but she knows how to behave and be calm when it is necessary to be.

adoptionList.name: Cottom
adoptionList.description: Cotton is very affectionate, loves pampering and keeping company on the lap is special for the sofa!.

adoptionList.name: Atenea
adoptionList.description: Athena is an abandoned homemade cat, she is very good, calm and affectionate and she has very soft hair!

adoptionList.name: Miko
adoptionList.description: Rescued from some gardens being a baby where the neighbors do not want the cats and call the kennel continuously. Sometimes it's a little scary.

adoptionList.name: Caty
adoptionList.description: This little girl is very sociable and affectionate, she never tires of giving and asking for pampering. His meow is very funny.

adoptionList.name: Anibal
adoptionList.description: Character:Distrustful, elusive, easily startled and does not trust people, but it is not a cat that tries to scratch or bite

adoptionList.name: Tanita
adoptionList.description: She was born from one of the females rescued from the park of 100 rabbits.She does not let herself get caught and she is scary with people. However, he gets along very well with other rabbits. She needs to be adopted by someone who looks for another rabbit and does not mind that she is not very affectionate
